<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Multigamer - Snake Game</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        #nicknameScreen, #instructionsScreen, #gameScreen, #gameOverScreen {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        #gameCanvas {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .joystick {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .joystick div {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 5px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="nicknameScreen">
        <h1>Bem-vindo ao Multigamer!</h1>
        <input type="text" id="nicknameInput" placeholder="Digite seu nickname">
        <button class="btn" onclick="showInstructions()">Próximo</button>
    </div>
    <div id="instructionsScreen">
        <h1>Instruções</h1>
        <p>Use o joystick para controlar a cobrinha. Coma os alimentos para ganhar pontos. Se a cobrinha bater nas paredes ou em si mesma, é game over.</p>
        <button class="btn" onclick="startGame()">Próximo</button>
    </div>
    <div id="gameScreen">
        <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="300" height="300"></canvas>
        <div class="joystick">
            <div onclick="moveSnake('up')">↑</div>
            <div onclick="moveSnake('left')">←</div>
            <div onclick="moveSnake('down')">↓</div>
            <div onclick="moveSnake('right')">→</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="gameOverScreen">
        <h1>Game Over</h1>
        <p>Sua pontuação: <span id="finalScore"></span></p>
        <button class="btn" onclick="showNextGame()">Próximo Minigame</button>
    </div>

    <script src="snake.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
</body>
</html>
